(as a result?)

20:46:54.618539 fe80::3e8c:1d09 > fe80::3e8c:1d09: icmp6: time exceeded in-transit for fe80::3e18:401b
20:46:54.618588 fe80::3e8c:1d09 > fe80::3e8c:1d09: icmp6: time exceeded in-transit for fe80::3e18:401b [hlim 1]
